DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nCome join us for some trivia and pizza
 . They sell pizza by the slice on trivia nights making it easy to hangout 
 and have fun!\n\nI'll be at an outside table.\n\n8175 Gravenstein Hwy\, Co
 tati\, CA 94931
